headline: FirstEnergy (FE) Upgraded to ‘Outperform’ at Wolfe Research
summary: FirstEnergy Corp. (NYSE:FE) is included among the 10 High Yield Utility Stocks to Buy in 2026. FirstEnergy Corp.
